      <title>西班牙 Europastry 因选举波动推迟 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/spain-s-europastry-puts-ipo-plans-on-hold-citing-french-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙烘焙公司 Europastry SA 推迟了首次公开募股 (IPO)，成为该地区 IPO 复苏举步维艰之际最新一家停止上市计划的欧洲公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/spain-s-europastry-puts-ipo-plans-on-hold-citing-french-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 18:28:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rite Aid 避免全面关闭，重组计划获批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/rite-aid-averts-total-closure-wins-restructuring-plan-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rite Aid Corp. 的重组计划获得法院批准，已获准退出破产程序，该计划旨在通过将业务控制权移交给主要债权人，拯救这家陷入困境的连锁药店，避免其被清算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/rite-aid-averts-total-closure-wins-restructuring-plan-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 18:25:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登：“我知道如何做好这份工作”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/biden-i-know-how-to-do-this-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他致力于赢得11月的大选，在与共和党人唐纳德·特朗普的辩论惨败后，他无视民主党知名人士要求他下台的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/biden-i-know-how-to-do-this-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 18:14:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
