      <title>哥伦比亚央行无视 Petro 政策，将利率下调至 11.25%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/colombian-central-bank-defies-petro-and-cuts-key-rate-to-11-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚央行周五将基准利率下调半个百分点至 11.25%，不顾政府加快货币宽松步伐以重振经济增长的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/colombian-central-bank-defies-petro-and-cuts-key-rate-to-11-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 18:05:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
